<!-- wax seal -->
	</address></ab>

            </div>
			
			<div>
<lb/><p>The <term type="occupation">mayor</term> got 12 varieties together after the
<lb/>above was penned <unclear cert="low">one however</unclear> is the <term type="plant_foodstuff">mango</term><!-- I'm having trouble reading this line. MB -->
<lb/>He will be able to do much more. I have
<lb/>collected at different times upwards of 30
<lb/>kinds of <term type="plant_foodstuff">fruits</term> and <term type="plant_foodstuff">berries</term>. I exclude from <w>the<gap extent="1" unit="chars"/><supplied>m</supplied></w>
<lb/>those which though eaten are <w><choice><sic>disagreable</sic><corr>disagreeable</corr></choice></w>. <w>On<gap extent="1" unit="chars"/><supplied>e</supplied></w>
<lb/>the <term type="occupation">Mayor</term> now sends is used for making a 
<lb/><term type="foodstuff">sweet meat</term> or <term type="foodstuff">preserve</term> as <term type="foodstuff">almonds</term> are. 
</p>
			</div>
